    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1922-09-16T12:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1922-09-16T12:00:00-05:00" n="512"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d512">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">815.00/2476: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Minister in Honduras</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morales</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Tegucigalpa</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1922-09-16T11:00:00-06:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">September 16, 1922—11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received September 18—9:20 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>76. Revolutionary movement headed by Francisco Martínez Funes completely
                    overthrown. Government forces killing 56 and capturing 78 men. Government in
                    full control of the situation.</p>
                <p>The President requests that the <hi rend="italic">Tacoma</hi> remain at Truxillo
                    for several days.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Morales</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
